  "detail": {
    "endLabelIds": "",
    "endLabelNames": "",
    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体交易管理规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1354422683511537664",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 3; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 20pt; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 3;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">您好，为适应业务发展需求，将针对<span style=\"color: black;\">《</span></span><span style=\"color: #2100ff;\"><a style=\"color: #2100ff;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1090224406216708096\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东开放平台个人/个体交易管理规则</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">》</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">进行调整。现进行规则公示，公示期：2026年4月10日- 2026年4月26日，规则预计于 2026年4月27日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 3; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心调整点：新增</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">延迟发货、缺货无货、未发货订单积压、发货异常等场景违约金档位标准<strong>，新增</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; font-weight: normal;\">违约金档位</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">规则解读<strong>，</strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">修订</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">虚假发货异常情形。详见下文。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 3; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一、修订虚假发货异常情形</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">修订前：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">赠品先发，实际主商品晚发（商家上传订单物流单号非主商品物流单号）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">修订后：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">商家上传的物流单号非订单主商品真实运单号，如后台上传A运单，实际发B运单。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二、新增延迟发货、缺货无货、未发货订单积压、发货异常等场景违约金档位标准</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">1.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">延迟发货、缺货无货</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（1）订单实际发货时间超最晚发货时间3天及以内：扣收违约金6元/单</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">（M1档）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（2）订单实际发货时间超最晚发货时间3天以上：扣收违约金20元/单</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">（M1档）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"> ；同时根据商家发货超时严重程度，扣除物流分0.1-5分。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（3）商家因自身原因、缺货无货等因素，确定无法按时发货时，订单最晚发货时间前：扣收违约金10元/单</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">（M1档）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">；订单超最晚发货时间后：扣收违约金20元/单</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">（M1档）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（4）若订单超最晚发货时间7天仍未发货，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">再按订单实付金额所在区间扣除违约金</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">，最低20元/单，最高500元/单。</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 800px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">订单实付金额</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违约金</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违约金档位</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">500</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元（不含）以内</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">20</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元/单</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">M1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">500</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元（含）到2000元（不含）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">50</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元/单</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">2000</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元（含）到5000元（不含）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">200</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元/单</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">M2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">5000</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元（含）以上</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">500</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元/单</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2.&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">未发货订单积压</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">轻微积压扣除违约金50元/次</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">（M1档）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">；严重积压扣除违约金</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">200</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">元/次</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">（M2档）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">。为保障消费者体验、控制商家资损，自然月内，轻微、严重积压累计次数达极值时（取历史自然月轻微、严重积压违规次数最多的前20%作为极值基准值），在商家再次触发轻微、严重积压时，将直接限售24小时。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">（二）发货异常</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">1.&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">未按承诺使用发货方式</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">若商家向消费者承诺发货形式与实际发货形式不符，京东有权视违规程度对商家扣除违约金</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">200</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元到800元/次（M2档）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2.&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">未按承诺时效履约</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">若商家在商品标题、主图、详情页等承诺送达时间但实际未能履约，京东有权对商家扣除违约金10元/单</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">（M1档）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">3.&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">违规加收运费</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">若存在包邮商品商家要求消费者额外支付运费才能发货，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">京东有权视违规程度对商家扣除违约金200元到800元/次（M2档）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">（三） 配送异常</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20.15pt; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">若商家物流停滞违规属实，京东有权对商家扣除5元/单的违约金</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">（M1档）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">；在月度考核周期内，当成交单量大于100单，且物流停滞单量的占比大于5%时，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">京东有权视违规程度对商家扣除违约金200元到800元/次（M2档）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">若商家未规范使用厂家自送、用户自提</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、无需物流<span style=\"background: white;\">发货方式违规属实，京东有权视违规程度对商家扣除违约金</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">200</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元到800元/次（M2档）。</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">若产生物流纠纷客诉问题（如周期内客诉占比较高或引发投诉及舆情等情形），京东有权永久关闭三种发货模式。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">（四） 签收异常</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20.15pt; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">若商家签收异常违规属实，京东有权视违规程度</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">对商家按订单实付金额所在区间扣除违约金。</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 800px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">订单实付金额</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违约金</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违约金档位</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">500</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元（不含）以内</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">20</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元/单</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">M1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">500</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元（含）到2000元（不含）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">50</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元/单</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">2000</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元（含）到5000元（不含）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">200</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元/单</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">M2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">5000</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元（含）以上</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">500</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">元/单</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">（五）严重违规</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">若店铺发生虚假发货、虚假轨迹或欺诈发货行为，京东有权视违规程度对商家及其关联店铺采取处置措施，包含扣除违约金、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">延长自动确认收货时间、<span style=\"background: white;\">冻结扣除店铺资金（包括货款、保证金等)、扣除违规所得资金、管控、限权、关店等处置措施。 其中，管控包括但不限于违规商品下架且禁止上架、降低店铺星级、全店商品流量降权/屏蔽、延长结算周期、加收风险保证金等；限权包括但不限于限制新品标识、限制使用厂自模式、店铺清退等。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; background: white; word-break: break-all; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">其中，违约金扣除详细情况如下：</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 800px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 49.25pt; background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"66\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违规场景</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 188.65pt; background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"252\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违规情况</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违约金档位</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 49.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"66\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">虚假发货</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">虚假轨迹</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 188.65pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"252\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">订单存在消费者投诉或者负向反馈行为；</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">M2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">档位</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">根据订单实付金额不同，扣除200元、500元或800元</span> </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 188.65pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"252\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">单日虚假发货或虚假轨迹违规订单总量达到5单且占当日发货订单总量超过5%；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">产生舆情事件或对京东平台造成负面影响的情形；</span> </span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">M4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">：店铺近14天成交金额20%，最低300元，最高100,000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 49.25pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"66\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #f5222d;\">欺诈发货</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 188.65pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"252\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left